  "detailed_description": "<strong>DJ SIMULATOR</strong> is a first-person simulation where you can live out your dream DJ life.<br><br>Create your <strong>PERFECT DJ</strong> with the <strong>DJ CUSTOMIZER!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798880/extras/character_creator.gif?t=1759829240\" /></span><br><br>Learn <strong>REAL</strong> DJing techniques using the customizable DJ decks and laptop!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798880/extras/ce3d2cf8473056659b2fe0ef7095ef18.poster.avif?t=1759829240\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798880/extras/ce3d2cf8473056659b2fe0ef7095ef18.webm?t=1759829240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798880/extras/ce3d2cf8473056659b2fe0ef7095ef18.mp4?t=1759829240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play at randomly generated gigs!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798880/extras/2cf138d20f0c47caf6fdad7060e12ffb.poster.avif?t=1759829240\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798880/extras/2cf138d20f0c47caf6fdad7060e12ffb.webm?t=1759829240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798880/extras/2cf138d20f0c47caf6fdad7060e12ffb.mp4?t=1759829240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The crowd responds to your performance</strong>: each NPC has individual desires and traits, you will need to learn your crowd to impress them!<br><br>Climb the ranks of fame - get paid more per event and unlock bigger and better venues! Start out as a supporting act and become a headliner!<br><br>Includes an in built library of original music, custom music importing from your own storage and Steam Workshop!",
